name: Hollow Pixels 22 - Mammal
description:
In our world, Orca jump out of the water for various reasons:  to search for member of their pods, to watch for preys, to celebrate a good hunt, etc…
Here, the resemblance of this Hollow Pixels creature, referred to as « Mammal », with an Orca is too obvious to be ignored. 
What could be the reason of Mammal’s jump?

IG&Twitter:  @dacosta_works
